    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26.29-30_0001"/>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>2-6-58</dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I want to Thank you once again for speaking to my classes in Creative Writing as Stephens College on January 18th. Many students have expressed great pleasure in The opportunity to hear you speak and several of my
                
                <fw type="curatorial">29</fw>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26.29-30_0002"/>
                
                    colleagues have written me to compliment my choice of guests for my class. I thought you might be interested in The enclosed clipping which appeared in The student newspaper a week after you spoke. All my best wishes to you and your family.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Sincerely,</salute>
                
                    <signed>Charles Madden</signed>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
            
            
            <div1 type="envelope">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26.29-30_0003"/>
                
                <ab type="return">
                    <hi rend="caps">C.</hi> Ma<unclear cert="high">dden</unclear>
                    Stephens College
                    Columbia, Mo.
                </ab>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">30</fw>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    COLUMBIA MO.
                    FEB 7
                    130 PM
                    1958
                    
                    P<unclear cert="high">R</unclear>AY <unclear cert="high">F</unclear>OR PEACE
                </ab>
